{"tid":755781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒隆家族場外大手減持小米   套現21.3億元","createTime":"2018-07-25T12:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T11:30:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53a09a4aaa0a3e2729d7e8837c1462c2dc891665","tid":755781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180725/58483938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483938&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9507e42d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483938&h=65029bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180725/58483938</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532498590_d7be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532498590_d7be.jpg&h=38938e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n☭小米☭(1810)上市不足一個月，遭主要股東以上市價17元，在場外大手減持1.25億股。<br />\n<br />\n聯交所披露權益顯示，TMT General上周五(20日)於場外減持☭小米☭1.25億股，每股作價17元，套現21.33億元，持股量由18.72%降至17.93%。☭小米☭7月18至24日，連跌4個交易日，累挫15.4%。今日最☭新報☭18.36元，升0.65%，成交8.9億元。<br />\n<br />\nTMT General間接控制由恒隆集團(010)董事長陳啟宗弟弟陳樂宗、☭小米☭非執董劉芹創辦的晨興集團，為☭小米☭第二大股東。"},{"pid":"a48a41336f4736a874c75b6843cd4e8467723483","tid":755781,"uid":36178,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"無禁售期？"},{"pid":"59eb3dade91f235b185e07ed15510fbe3628d0a2","tid":755781,"uid":54884,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"有18%咁多 二十幾億股咪三百幾億  竟然會冇禁售期"},{"pid":"b637ebdb340bdd61e6f9776bd32509886b339018","tid":755781,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T13